#!/bin/rc
# Similar to running "new CMD", but asynchronous.
# See watch options.
#
# Is it better than running |new, and entering command in tag?
# - Bit easier to kill, with Kill or Del; but I don't kill often.
# - Deleting window kills the process.
# - Don't get the blue box while running, but on completion the text will
#   be selected.

watch -sn $* &
